WEBVTT

00:00:58.704 --> 00:01:02.042
that were there were slightly bigger
than the eight-by-seven cell.

00:01:02.551 --> 00:01:05.146
But being in that cell
as he awaited the executioner --

00:01:05.170 --> 00:01:07.463
because in prison,
he did not have a name --

00:01:08.292 --> 00:01:10.132
Manson was known by a number.

00:01:10.625 --> 00:01:11.894
He was just a statistic.

00:01:13.751 --> 00:01:15.815
He did not know how long he would wait.

00:01:16.323 --> 00:01:18.077
The wait could have been a minute,

00:01:18.101 --> 00:01:20.371
the executioner could have come
the next minute,

00:01:20.395 --> 00:01:21.768
the next day,

00:01:21.792 --> 00:01:23.513
or it could have taken 30 years.

00:01:25.511 --> 00:01:26.845
The wait had no end.

00:01:28.194 --> 00:01:31.075
